This paper is about visual tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms to analyze tracking behavior, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation of tracking algorithms, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
